{{Infobox Berry |name = Qualot |image = [[File:Qualot.png]] |caption = Even in places of constant rain and high humidity, this Berry's plant grows healthy and strong. |growtime = 1h 20m 0s |harvest = 22 berries |replant = 20% |points = 550 |flavor = {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 10 }} '''Qualot''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 10, but no more than 15 points of spicy, sweet and sour and 0 points of all other flavours. The [[Cheri]], [[Pecha]] and [[Aspear]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry.
